Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.85,0:00:19.81,Main,,0,0,0,,- THIS IS FOR REAL.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.89,0:00:21.44,Main,,0,0,0,,OKAY, I'LL SEE\NYOU LATER, BYE.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.81,0:00:23.73,Main,,0,0,0,,- Mizuki: I KNEW IT.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.82,0:00:26.19,Main,,0,0,0,,MINAMI HAS A THING\NFOR AKIHISA.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.28,0:00:27.23,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( screams )
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.32,0:00:28.40,Main,,0,0,0,,- THIS IS FOR REAL.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.49,0:00:29.49,Main,,0,0,0,,I'LL SEE YOU IN HELL.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.57,0:00:31.57,Main,,0,0,0,,TAKE THE FUGITIVE AWAY.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.66,0:00:33.87,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( grumbling )\N- SHE LIKES HIM.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.95,0:00:38.08,Main,,0,0,0,,SHE, LIKE,\NLIKE-LIKES HIM.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.75,0:00:43.38,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( singing in Japanese )
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.50,0:02:10.25,Main,,0,0,0,,- Fukuhara: A WEEK\NAFTER TRAINING CAMP,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.34,0:02:13.38,Main,,0,0,0,,THE YEAR-TWO BOY'S SUSPENSION\NIS FINALLY OVER.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.47,0:02:15.22,Main,,0,0,0,,- YUUJI.\N- YEAH?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.30,0:02:18.64,Main,,0,0,0,,WHAT IS IT?\N( screams )
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.72,0:02:19.89,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU DODGED ME.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.97,0:02:21.18,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU WERE ABOUT\NTO HEAD BUTT ME.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.27,0:02:22.56,Main,,0,0,0,,I'M NOT JUST GONNA\NSIT THERE AND TAKE IT.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.64,0:02:23.85,Main,,0,0,0,,- I WAS ONLY\NTRYING TO KISS YOU.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.94,0:02:26.69,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU WERE WHAT?\NOKAY, NOW STAY RIGHT THERE.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.77,0:02:29.23,Main,,0,0,0,,PUT YOUR HANDS BEHIND YOUR HEAD\NAND EXPLAIN SLOWLY.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.31,0:02:32.40,Main,,0,0,0,,- A KISS, MOUTH TO MOUTH,\NLIP TO LIP.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.49,0:02:35.28,Main,,0,0,0,,IT'S ONLY NATURAL CONSIDERING\NWE'RE ENGAGED TO BE MARRIED.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.36,0:02:37.12,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT? NO.\NI KNOW WHAT A KISS IS.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.20,0:02:38.70,Main,,0,0,0,,WHAT I WAS TRYING TO ASK YOU\NIS WHY YOU--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.78,0:02:40.45,Main,,0,0,0,,( groans )\N- WHEN, WHERE, AND WITH WHOM
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.53,0:02:42.33,Main,,0,0,0,,DID YOU KISS?\N- I JUST KNOW WHAT IT IS.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.41,0:02:44.58,Main,,0,0,0,,I NEVER SAID\NI ACTUALLY KISSED ANYONE.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.66,0:02:46.75,Main,,0,0,0,,- OH, WELL, THAT'S GOOD.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.83,0:02:49.54,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU'RE KILLING ME.  WHAT'S ALL\NTHIS HEAD-BUTT-KISSING CRAP
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.63,0:02:51.46,Main,,0,0,0,,ABOUT IN THE FIRST PLACE?\N- THOSE TWO.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.55,0:02:53.38,Main,,0,0,0,,THEY WERE KISSING\NA MOMENT AGO.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.47,0:02:56.09,Main,,0,0,0,,- SERIOUSLY?\NWHAT'S HE THINKING?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.18,0:02:57.76,Main,,0,0,0,,HE KNEW THOSE GUYS\NWOULD KILL HIM FOR THAT.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.84,0:02:59.80,Main,,0,0,0,,IT'S LIKE HE'S ACTUALLY\NGETTING STUPIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.89,0:03:02.60,Main,,0,0,0,,BY THE FLIPPING MINUTE.\N- I APOLOGIZE.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.68,0:03:04.27,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT?\N- WHILE YOU WERE SLEEPING,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.35,0:03:06.48,Main,,0,0,0,,I MIGHT HAVE DONE SOMETHING.\N- AHA!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.56,0:03:08.31,Main,,0,0,0,,- LOOKS LIKE WE HAVE\NANOTHER HERETIC OVER HERE.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.40,0:03:09.65,Main,,0,0,0,,- ALL RIGHT, TAKE HIM IN.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.73,0:03:11.40,Main,,0,0,0,,- AH! HEY, STOP IT.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.48,0:03:12.73,Main,,0,0,0,,I DIDN'T EVEN DO ANYTHING!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.82,0:03:14.11,Main,,0,0,0,,LET ME GO!\N- I'M A NAUGHTY GIRL.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.19,0:03:15.69,Main,,0,0,0,,ALTHOUGH, ALL I DID\NWAS KISS HIM ON THE CHEEK.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.03,0:03:19.28,Main,,0,0,0,,- MEN, TELL THEM\NWHERE WE ARE.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.37,0:03:22.16,Main,,0,0,0,,- THE COURT FOR PASSING\NVIOLENT JUDGMENT.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.24,0:03:23.33,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT HAPPENS TO TRAITORS?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.41,0:03:25.25,Main,,0,0,0,,- THE DEATH PENALTY AWAITS.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.33,0:03:28.83,Main,,0,0,0,,- WONDERFUL! AND NOW,\NLET THE INQUISITION BEGIN.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.92,0:03:31.04,Main,,0,0,0,,- HEY, YUUJI, WHY DID\NTHEY BRING YOU HERE?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.13,0:03:32.42,Main,,0,0,0,,- BECAUSE OF YOU, YOU JERK!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.50,0:03:35.34,Main,,0,0,0,,- READ THE CHARGES, PLEASE.\N- THEY ARE AS FOLLOWS.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.42,0:03:38.38,Main,,0,0,0,,AKIHISA YOSHI\NSHALL BE KNOWN AS "A."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.47,0:03:41.05,Main,,0,0,0,,MINAMI SHIMADA SHALL\NBE KNOWN AS "FLAT CHEST."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.14,0:03:44.06,Main,,0,0,0,,"A" IS CHARGED WITH AN ACT OF\NDISLOYALTY TO OUR DOCTRINE.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.14,0:03:46.94,Main,,0,0,0,,EARLIER THIS MORNING,\N"A" WAS CAUGHT WITH "FLAT CHEST"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.02,0:03:49.35,Main,,0,0,0,,AS HE SEXUALLY ASSAULTED\NHER ON THE MOUTH.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.44,0:03:52.02,Main,,0,0,0,,OUR FELLOW MEMBERS DUTIFULLY\NCAPTURED HIM AT THAT TIME.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.11,0:03:54.40,Main,,0,0,0,,THE RELATIONSHIP BETWEEN\N"A" AND "FLAT CHEST"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.48,0:03:55.99,Main,,0,0,0,,CALLS FOR A THOROUGH\NINVESTIGATION.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.07,0:03:58.15,Main,,0,0,0,,"A" SHOULD SUFFER\NTHE CONSEQUENCES
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.24,0:04:00.87,Main,,0,0,0,,AND "FLAT CHEST" SHOULD HAVE\NA WATCHFUL EYE KEPT ON HER
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.95,0:04:02.20,Main,,0,0,0,,IN THE FUTURE.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.28,0:04:03.78,Main,,0,0,0,,- JUST STATE THE CONCLUSION!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.87,0:04:07.37,Main,,0,0,0,,- WE'RE JEALOUS OF HIM\NBECAUSE HE WAS KISSING A GIRL!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.46,0:04:08.87,Main,,0,0,0,,- DEATH PENALTY IT IS.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.96,0:04:10.67,Main,,0,0,0,,- AKI, DO YOU HAVE\NANY IDEA WHAT'S GOING ON?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.75,0:04:12.34,Main,,0,0,0,,- NO, I WASN'T\NPAYING ATTENTION.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.42,0:04:14.96,Main,,0,0,0,,- DOESN'T SOMETHING SEEM WEIRD\NTO YOU ABOUT ALL THIS?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.05,0:04:16.59,Main,,0,0,0,,- HMM.\N- DO YOU REMEMBER
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.67,0:04:18.30,Main,,0,0,0,,THE LAST TIME\NYOU SAW MINAMI?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.38,0:04:20.55,Main,,0,0,0,,- I THINK IT WAS THAT LAST NIGHT\NAT THE TRAINING CAMP.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.63,0:04:21.68,Main,,0,0,0,,- OKAY, WHAT HAPPENED?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.76,0:04:23.43,Main,,0,0,0,,- WELL, AFTER EVERYONE\NFELL ASLEEP,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.51,0:04:25.81,Main,,0,0,0,,SHE, LIKE, RANDOMLY\NCAME UP TO ME.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.89,0:04:28.14,Main,,0,0,0,,- SERIOUSLY? AND YOU DIDN'T\NTHINK THAT WAS STRANGE AT ALL?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.23,0:04:30.60,Main,,0,0,0,,- I FIGURED, YOU KNOW,\NSHE JUST WANTED TO KILL ME.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.69,0:04:33.15,Main,,0,0,0,,- SO THINK.  BEFORE THAT,\NDID YOU SAY ANYTHING TO HER?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.23,0:04:35.69,Main,,0,0,0,,- LET ME THINK.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.77,0:04:38.44,Main,,0,0,0,,THERE WAS THAT ONE THING.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.53,0:04:39.99,Main,,0,0,0,,( gasps )
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.07,0:04:43.03,Main,,0,0,0,,- IS EVERYTHING OKAY, DUDE?\N- YEAH, I'M GOOD.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.12,0:04:44.87,Main,,0,0,0,,- WELL, WHAT DID YOU\NTALK TO HER ABOUT?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.95,0:04:46.87,Main,,0,0,0,,- A KIND OF\NLOVE-CONFESSION THING.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.95,0:04:49.66,Main,,0,0,0,,- WAIT, SHE CONFESSED TO YOU?\N- NO, I DID THE CONFESSING.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.75,0:04:50.92,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( grunts )\N- ( screams )
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.00,0:04:53.33,Main,,0,0,0,,- THAT DIDN'T SEEM\NA LITTLE WEIRD TO YOU?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.42,0:04:56.50,Main,,0,0,0,,- HERETIC AKIHISA YOSHI,\NWILL YOU REPENT YOUR SIN
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.59,0:04:58.80,Main,,0,0,0,,AND ACCEPT THE RULING\NPLACED AGAINST YOU?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.88,0:05:01.22,Main,,0,0,0,,- DEPENDS ON THE RULING.\N- YOUR SENTENCE
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.30,0:05:03.22,Main,,0,0,0,,IS A SPECIAL BUNGEE JUMP.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.30,0:05:04.51,Main,,0,0,0,,- CAN YOU TELL ME,\NLIKE, WHAT KIND
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.60,0:05:07.01,Main,,0,0,0,,OF SPECIAL BUNGEE JUMP?\N- I DON'T WANT TO CAUSE
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.10,0:05:09.77,Main,,0,0,0,,UNNECESSARY CONCERN,\NBUT I WILL GIVE YOU A HINT.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.85,0:05:12.48,Main,,0,0,0,,THINK SKYDIVING\NWITHOUT A PARACHUTE.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.56,0:05:15.23,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( screams )\NTHAT'S NOT A HINT.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.31,0:05:17.02,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU'RE TELLING ME\NYOU WANT ME TO BUNGEE JUMP
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.11,0:05:18.65,Main,,0,0,0,,WITHOUT A CHORD?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.19,0:05:21.65,Main,,0,0,0,,LOOK, IT'S HIMEJI!\NOVER HERE!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.74,0:05:24.87,Main,,0,0,0,,- I HAD A SNEAKING SUSPICION\NMINAMI LIKED AKIHISA.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.95,0:05:26.24,Main,,0,0,0,,I GUESS I WAS RIGHT.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.33,0:05:28.29,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHY ARE YOU STILL\NACTING LIKE THAT?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.56,0:05:54.48,Main,,0,0,0,,- THEY JUST EXCHANGED WORDS\NWITH THEIR EYES!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.56,0:05:57.06,Main,,0,0,0,,- NOW I'LL NEVER HAVE\NA CHANCE WITH "FLAT CHEST."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.15,0:05:58.82,Main,,0,0,0,,- JUST LIKE\NHIMEJI AND HIDEYOSHI,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.90,0:06:00.36,Main,,0,0,0,,MINAMI HAS FALLEN\NUNDER HIS SPELL.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.44,0:06:01.82,Main,,0,0,0,,BEWARE THE DEVIL\NKNOWN AS AKI!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.90,0:06:04.15,Main,,0,0,0,,- HEY, AKI, HOW ARE YOU?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.24,0:06:06.53,Main,,0,0,0,,- OH, HEY, WHAT'S UP?\N- WOULD YOU MIND--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.62,0:06:08.79,Main,,0,0,0,,I MEAN, IS IT OKAY IF I SIT\NAT YOUR TABLE WITH YOU?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.87,0:06:11.33,Main,,0,0,0,,- HUH?\N- MINE IS BROKEN, SO...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.41,0:06:13.92,Main,,0,0,0,,- OH, YEAH, THAT SUCKS.\NSURE.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.00,0:06:15.25,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU'RE THE BEST.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.29,0:06:18.92,Main,,0,0,0,,ARE YOU SICK?\N'CAUSE YOU'RE SWEATING.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.00,0:06:21.51,Main,,0,0,0,,- NO, JUST FEELING\NCLAUSTROPHOBIC.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.59,0:06:23.76,Main,,0,0,0,,- WELL, THE TABLE\NIS KIND OF SMALL.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.84,0:06:25.51,Main,,0,0,0,,- YEAH, THAT'S TRUE.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.59,0:06:28.64,Main,,0,0,0,,- SO, UM, I WAS JUST THINKING\NTHAT WE COULD MAYBE--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.72,0:06:30.14,Main,,0,0,0,,I DON'T KNOW.\NWE COULD, YOU KNOW,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.22,0:06:31.39,Main,,0,0,0,,HAVE OUR LUNCH TOGETHER?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.47,0:06:32.98,Main,,0,0,0,,I MADE SOMETHING SPECIAL\NFOR YOU TODAY.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.06,0:06:34.85,Main,,0,0,0,,- DARLING, WHAT EXACTLY\NARE YOU DOING?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.94,0:06:36.31,Main,,0,0,0,,- ELBOW IN MY FACE!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.40,0:06:38.36,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU SHOULDN'T SIT SO CLOSE\NTO THIS FILTHY TRASH.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.44,0:06:40.32,Main,,0,0,0,,HE'S GROSS!\N- WELL MY TABLE'S BROKEN.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.40,0:06:41.99,Main,,0,0,0,,AND IT ISN'T LIKE\NI HAVE MUCH OF A CHOICE.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.07,0:06:43.36,Main,,0,0,0,,- SO WHAT? THAT DOESN'T MEAN\NYOU HAVE TO SIT
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.44,0:06:44.57,Main,,0,0,0,,NEXT TO SUCH\NA WASTE OF SPACE.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.65,0:06:46.28,Main,,0,0,0,,- MINAMI LIKES AKIHISA.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.36,0:06:47.53,Main,,0,0,0,,MINAMI LIKES AKIHISA.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.62,0:06:48.99,Main,,0,0,0,,- I DIDN'T WANT\NTO BOTHER MIZUKI
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.07,0:06:50.41,Main,,0,0,0,,BECAUSE SHE ACTUALLY STUDIES.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.49,0:06:53.00,Main,,0,0,0,,I MEAN, TALK ABOUT RUDE, RIGHT?\NAKIHISA'S DIFFERENT.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.08,0:06:55.25,Main,,0,0,0,,EVERYONE KNOWS HE'S GONNA\NGET BAD GRADES ANYWAY.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.33,0:06:57.92,Main,,0,0,0,,- I'M STARTING TO FEEL LIKE\NYOU'RE NOT COMPLIMENTING ME.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.00,0:07:00.13,Main,,0,0,0,,- NO WAY! I CANNOT ALLOW
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.21,0:07:02.13,Main,,0,0,0,,THIS DISGUSTING PIG TO THINK\NYOU MADE LUNCH FOR HIM!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.21,0:07:04.38,Main,,0,0,0,,FRIED CHICKEN WITH YOUR\NHOMEMADE SPECIAL SAUCE
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.47,0:07:06.18,Main,,0,0,0,,THAT YOU MADE THIS MORNING.\NAND NOT TO MENTION
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.26,0:07:07.97,Main,,0,0,0,,THE SUPER EXPENSIVE\NGROUND BEEF HAMBURGERS.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.05,0:07:10.35,Main,,0,0,0,,AND THEN THERE'S\NTHE ORGANIC POTATO SALAD.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.43,0:07:11.51,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU'RE SUCH A STALKER.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.60,0:07:12.81,Main,,0,0,0,,HOW COULD YOU\NPOSSIBLY KNOW THAT?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.89,0:07:14.52,Main,,0,0,0,,- OH, GUESS WHAT'S\NON TOP OF THE RICE.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.60,0:07:17.06,Main,,0,0,0,,A DAMN HEART!\N- MIHARU, SHUT YOUR MOUTH!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.14,0:07:19.23,Main,,0,0,0,,( sighs )
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.31,0:07:21.65,Main,,0,0,0,,LISTEN TO ME.\NI'VE BEEN PATIENT WITH YOU
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.73,0:07:23.11,Main,,0,0,0,,UP UNTIL NOW,\NBUT I REALLY NEED YOU
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.19,0:07:24.61,Main,,0,0,0,,TO STOP DOING\NTHIS KIND OF STUFF,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.69,0:07:28.70,Main,,0,0,0,,BECAUSE-- WELL, BECAUSE\NAKI AND I HAVE STARTED DATING.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.70,0:07:30.99,Main,,0,0,0,,- DEFLECTIVE MAP FLIP!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.16,0:07:34.29,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( growling )
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.37,0:07:35.58,Main,,0,0,0,,- THAT'S JUST THE WAY IT IS.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.66,0:07:37.75,Main,,0,0,0,,I HOPE YOU UNDERSTAND.\N- I DON'T! YOU AND I ARE
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.83,0:07:39.21,Main,,0,0,0,,GONNA GET MARRIED\NAND NAME OUR DAUGHTER MIRAI
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.29,0:07:40.38,Main,,0,0,0,,SO THE FIRST PART\NOF HER NAME
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.46,0:07:41.59,Main,,0,0,0,,SOUNDS LIKE THE FIRST PART\NOF YOURS BECAUSE
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.67,0:07:42.42,Main,,0,0,0,,THAT'S THE WAY\NIT'S SUPPOSED TO BE.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.50,0:07:43.59,Main,,0,0,0,,- HOLD IT RIGHT THERE!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.67,0:07:45.05,Main,,0,0,0,,WHAT ARE YOU GONNA NAME IT\NIF IT'S A BOY?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.13,0:07:47.13,Main,,0,0,0,,- I'M THINKING STEVEN\NSHOULD WORK OKAY.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.22,0:07:48.68,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU'RE MISSING\NSOMETHING IMPORTANT!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.76,0:07:50.05,Main,,0,0,0,,THE TWO OF US\NCAN'T MAKE A BABY!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.14,0:07:51.43,Main,,0,0,0,,- CLASS IS STARTING.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.51,0:07:53.39,Main,,0,0,0,,WHAT ARE YOU DOING IN HERE?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.47,0:07:55.10,Main,,0,0,0,,GO BACK TO YOUR\NCLASSROOM, SHIMIZU.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.18,0:07:57.60,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU NEED TO TURN AROUND\NAND WALK AWAY, NISHIMURA.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.69,0:07:59.48,Main,,0,0,0,,I'M DEALING WITH A MATTER\NOF LIFE AND DEATH.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.56,0:08:01.31,Main,,0,0,0,,- LIFE AND DEATH?\N- YES!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.40,0:08:03.02,Main,,0,0,0,,LIFE AND DEATH IN THAT\NI'M GONNA ANNIHILATE
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.11,0:08:04.48,Main,,0,0,0,,EVERY SLEAZY DIRTBAG IN HERE.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.57,0:08:05.86,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU ARE FORBIDDEN\NFROM ENTERING
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.94,0:08:07.61,Main,,0,0,0,,THIS CLASSROOM AGAIN, MISSY.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.70,0:08:10.41,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHY I OUGHTA!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.49,0:08:12.62,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU ALWAYS GET INTO\NSTUFF LIKE THIS.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.70,0:08:14.37,Main,,0,0,0,,- AT LEAST YOU GET\NSOME GOOD STORIES.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.45,0:08:17.37,Main,,0,0,0,,- LEAVE ME ALONE.  THIS TIME\NIT ISN'T EVEN MY FAULT.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.45,0:08:19.12,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU CAN DENY IT ALL YOU WANT,\NBUT WE'RE ABOUT
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.21,0:08:21.25,Main,,0,0,0,,TO GET IN TROUBLE\NBIG TIME BECAUSE OF YOU.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.33,0:08:22.71,Main,,0,0,0,,APPARENTLY, CLASS D's DECIDED
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.79,0:08:25.05,Main,,0,0,0,,THEY NEED TO CHALLENGE SOMEONE\NTO A SUMMONER TEST WAR.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.13,0:08:27.01,Main,,0,0,0,,- SO WHAT DO WE CARE IF THEY\NWANT TO FIGHT ANOTHER CLASS?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.09,0:08:28.59,Main,,0,0,0,,THAT DOESN'T HAVE\NANYTHING TO DO WITH US.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.68,0:08:30.76,Main,,0,0,0,,DUDE, THERE IS NO WAY\NYOU CAN PIN THAT ON ME.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.84,0:08:33.72,Main,,0,0,0,,- YES, I CAN, IF THE CLASS\NTHEY WANT TO FIGHT IS OURS.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.80,0:08:34.97,Main,,0,0,0,,- THAT DOESN'T MAKE SENSE.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.06,0:08:36.39,Main,,0,0,0,,WE HAVE THE WORST EQUIPMENT\NIN THE SCHOOL.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.47,0:08:38.06,Main,,0,0,0,,WHY WOULD THEY WANT TO FIGHT US\NOVER A BUNCH OF STUFF
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.14,0:08:39.69,Main,,0,0,0,,THAT'S CRAPPY? UNLESS...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.77,0:08:42.44,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU GUESSED IT.\NTHIS IS ALL MIHARU.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.52,0:08:43.94,Main,,0,0,0,,- SHE'S TRYING TO\NSWITCH OUR TABLES
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.02,0:08:46.36,Main,,0,0,0,,BACK TO CARDBOARD BOXES,\NJUST TO KEEP YOU AND MINAMI
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.44,0:08:47.65,Main,,0,0,0,,FROM SITTING\NNEXT TO EACH OTHER.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.74,0:08:49.57,Main,,0,0,0,,- BUT HOW COULD SHE GET\NEVERYONE IN CLASS D
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.65,0:08:51.36,Main,,0,0,0,,TO GO ALONG WITH HER?\NTHEY KNOW SHE'S CRAY-CRAY.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.45,0:08:54.24,Main,,0,0,0,,- WELL, WE ARE THE RINGLEADERS\NOF THE PEEKING INCIDENT.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.33,0:08:55.78,Main,,0,0,0,,NO WONDER THE GIRLS\NALREADY BELIEVE OUR CLASS
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.87,0:08:57.87,Main,,0,0,0,,IS THEIR SWORN ENEMY.\N- AND THEIR CLASS REP HIRAGA
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.95,0:08:59.04,Main,,0,0,0,,WON'T TRY TO\NFIGHT THEM ON IT.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.12,0:09:01.04,Main,,0,0,0,,MIHARU IS\NRIDICULOUSLY JEALOUS
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.12,0:09:02.83,Main,,0,0,0,,AND THE GIRLS ARE\NRIDICULOUSLY PISSED.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.92,0:09:04.54,Main,,0,0,0,,SO WHAT COULD HE DO?\N- BALLS.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.63,0:09:06.59,Main,,0,0,0,,- WITH THAT DAMN SUSPENSION,\NTHE GUYS HAVEN'T BEEN ABLE
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.67,0:09:07.96,Main,,0,0,0,,TO RECOVER THEIR\NSCORES YET EITHER.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.05,0:09:09.42,Main,,0,0,0,,EVEN HAVING\NHIMEJI ON OUR TEAM
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.51,0:09:10.92,Main,,0,0,0,,ISN'T GONNA HELP US\NAT THIS POINT.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.01,0:09:12.68,Main,,0,0,0,,- THERE'S ONLY\NONE WAY OUT, GUYS.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.76,0:09:13.80,Main,,0,0,0,,AVOID THE WAR.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.89,0:09:15.43,Main,,0,0,0,,- HOW ARE WE SUPPOSED\NTO DO THAT?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.51,0:09:17.26,Main,,0,0,0,,- I THINK IT'S UP TO\NYOU AND MINAMI NOW.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.35,0:09:19.10,Main,,0,0,0,,BUT BEFORE WE GET STARTED,\NTHERE'S ONE THING
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.18,0:09:20.64,Main,,0,0,0,,I'M CURIOUS ABOUT.\N- WHAT'S THAT?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.73,0:09:24.31,Main,,0,0,0,,- ARE YOU AND MINAMI DATING?\NLIKE FOR REAL DATING-DATING?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.40,0:09:25.82,Main,,0,0,0,,- AS FAR AS I CAN REMEMBER,\NWE'RE NOT,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.90,0:09:27.73,Main,,0,0,0,,BUT SHE MIGHT HAVE A GOOD REASON\NTO THINK WE ARE
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.82,0:09:30.32,Main,,0,0,0,,BECAUSE OF A TEXT MESSAGE\NI SORT OF ACCIDENTALLY SENT HER.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.40,0:09:31.70,Main,,0,0,0,,- AN ACCIDENTAL TEXT?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.78,0:09:33.24,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( gasps )\N- ( gasps )
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.32,0:09:35.58,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( sighs )\NWELL, THAT MAKES SENSE.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.66,0:09:37.62,Main,,0,0,0,,WHAT AKI DID WAS BAD ENOUGH,\NBUT THEN YUUJI
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.70,0:09:39.50,Main,,0,0,0,,HAD TO COME IN WITH\NSOME SUPER BAD TIMING
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.58,0:09:41.79,Main,,0,0,0,,AND MAKE THINGS EVEN WORSE.\N- THAT'S WHAT WAS GOING ON.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.87,0:09:44.38,Main,,0,0,0,,SORRY, AKI, I KNOW IT MUST SUCK,\NBUT LISTEN TO ME.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.46,0:09:46.17,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU HAVE REALLY\NGOT TO FIX THIS.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.25,0:09:48.25,Main,,0,0,0,,CLEAR THINGS UP\NWITH MINAMI LIKE ASAP.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.34,0:09:50.26,Main,,0,0,0,,MAYBE THEN MIHARU\NWILL CHILL OUT.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.34,0:09:51.63,Main,,0,0,0,,- OKAY.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.81,0:10:00.10,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT'S THE STORY, KOUTA?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.18,0:10:02.23,Main,,0,0,0,,DID YOU SEE MIHARU\NPLANT A WIRETAP DEVICE HERE?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.31,0:10:03.48,Main,,0,0,0,,- YEAH, BUT\NI MADE IT LOOK LIKE
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.56,0:10:04.73,Main,,0,0,0,,IT WAS BROKEN\NAND REMOVED IT.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.81,0:10:06.40,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT DID YOU WANT\NTO TALK TO ME ABOUT?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.48,0:10:08.86,Main,,0,0,0,,- WELL, DO YOU REMEMBER\NTHAT EMAIL I SENT YOU
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.94,0:10:11.32,Main,,0,0,0,,WHILE WE WERE STILL\NAT TRAINING CAMP?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.40,0:10:12.61,Main,,0,0,0,,I JUST WANTED\NTO LET YOU KNOW
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.70,0:10:14.32,Main,,0,0,0,,THAT YOU KIND OF\NGOT THE WRONG IDEA.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.41,0:10:16.49,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT?\N- YEAH, I'M AN IDIOT.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.57,0:10:18.83,Main,,0,0,0,,I MEANT TO SEND THAT EMAIL\NTO SOMEONE ELSE.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.91,0:10:21.29,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHO?\N- I'M PRETTY SURE IT WAS SUGAWA.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.37,0:10:22.66,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT?! ARE YOU TELLING ME
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.75,0:10:24.37,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU WERE GONNA CONFESS\NYOUR LOVE TO SUGAWA?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.46,0:10:25.92,Main,,0,0,0,,- I HAD A FEELING\NTHIS WOULD HAPPEN.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.00,0:10:28.34,Main,,0,0,0,,I MEAN, I KNOW YOU NEVER GAVE ME\NA REASON TO THINK OTHERWISE,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.42,0:10:30.09,Main,,0,0,0,,BUT I THOUGHT FOR SURE\NYOU LIKED GIRLS.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.17,0:10:31.76,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU WHAT?\NNO, IT'S NOT LIKE THAT.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.55,0:10:37.39,Main,,0,0,0,,- THAT IS JUST WRONG\NIN SO MANY WAYS.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.47,0:10:38.80,Main,,0,0,0,,- I KNOW.  I'M SORRY.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.89,0:10:40.64,Main,,0,0,0,,THE POINT IS\NI SENT IT ON ACCIDENT.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.72,0:10:42.60,Main,,0,0,0,,- TALK ABOUT A RELIEF.\NI ALWAYS SUSPECTED,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.68,0:10:44.06,Main,,0,0,0,,BUT I DIDN'T WANT\NTO EMBARRASS YOU.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.14,0:10:46.02,Main,,0,0,0,,I TOTES GET IT.\N- ( laughs )
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.10,0:10:47.90,Main,,0,0,0,,YEAH, YOU JUST KIND OF\NROLLED WITH IT, HUH?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.98,0:10:49.57,Main,,0,0,0,,- OH, PLEASE, THIS\NIS COMING FROM THE GUY
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.65,0:10:51.82,Main,,0,0,0,,WHO SENT A SUGGESTIVE EMAIL\NTO THE WRONG PERSON.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.90,0:10:53.70,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( all laugh )
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.78,0:10:55.45,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT ARE YOU GONNA DO\NABOUT MY FIRST KISS?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.53,0:10:57.57,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU SCREWED THAT UP FOR ME!\N- I'M SORRY.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.66,0:10:58.83,Main,,0,0,0,,I DIDN'T MEAN ANYTHING BY IT,\NI SWEAR.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.91,0:11:01.33,Main,,0,0,0,,- SORRY DOESN'T QUITE CUT IT,\NYOU JERK.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.41,0:11:03.20,Main,,0,0,0,,- YEAH, BUT--\N- WHAT?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.29,0:11:04.71,Main,,0,0,0,,- WELL...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.79,0:11:08.08,Main,,0,0,0,,IT WAS MY FIRST KISS TOO.\NWE'RE EVEN.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.17,0:11:10.00,Main,,0,0,0,,- YEAH, RIGHT.\NSHE IS SO NOT GONNA GO FOR THAT.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.09,0:11:13.13,Main,,0,0,0,,- I DIDN'T KNOW.\NSO, YEAH, I GUESS SO.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.21,0:11:15.72,Main,,0,0,0,,SURE, WE CAN CALL IT EVEN.\N- Yuuji: NO FREAKIN' WAY!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.80,0:11:17.43,Main,,0,0,0,,- HEY, SO I'M GONNA\NASK YOU SOMETHING,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.51,0:11:19.35,Main,,0,0,0,,BUT I DON'T WANT YOU\NTO GET ALL MAD AT ME.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.43,0:11:20.93,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT IS IT?\N- WELL, IT'S JUST--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.01,0:11:22.43,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU TOLD MIHARU\NTHAT WE WERE DATING,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.51,0:11:24.23,Main,,0,0,0,,SO DOES THAT MEAN\NTHAT YOU, YOU KNOW,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.31,0:11:26.06,Main,,0,0,0,,MAYBE YOU MIGHT HAVE--\NYOU KNOW, UH...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.14,0:11:27.56,Main,,0,0,0,,- NO! LIKE, NO.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.64,0:11:28.90,Main,,0,0,0,,SHE WASN'T GONNA\NGIVE UP LIKE EVER.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.98,0:11:30.82,Main,,0,0,0,,SO IT JUST SEEMED LIKE\NTHE LOGICAL THING TO SAY.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.90,0:11:31.98,Main,,0,0,0,,I DIDN'T, YOU KNOW, YOU KNOW.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.07,0:11:33.69,Main,,0,0,0,,IT WAS JUST SOME GOOD TIMING.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.78,0:11:36.61,Main,,0,0,0,,- DENIAL.COM.\N- SHE'S LYING TO HERSELF.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.70,0:11:38.57,Main,,0,0,0,,- OH, I WISH YOU\NWOULD HAVE TOLD ME.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.66,0:11:39.74,Main,,0,0,0,,I THOUGHT YOU, LIKE,\NLIKE-LIKED ME.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.82,0:11:40.95,Main,,0,0,0,,THAT'S SO WEIRD.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.03,0:11:43.16,Main,,0,0,0,,- YEAH, LIKE THAT EVER\NWOULD HAVE HAPPENED.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.24,0:11:44.87,Main,,0,0,0,,- YEAH, RIGHT.\NI COULDN'T FIGURE IT OUT.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.95,0:11:46.83,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU WERE ACTING LIKE\NSUCH A GIRL INSTEAD OF YOURSELF.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.91,0:11:50.09,Main,,0,0,0,,I FELT LIKE YOU WERE\NDISLOCATING MY ARM!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.17,0:11:52.67,Main,,0,0,0,,- WELL, AT LEAST THE MAIN\NCONFUSION HAS BEEN CLEARED UP.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.75,0:11:55.09,Main,,0,0,0,,- NOW ALL WE HAVE TO DO IS\NTELL CRAZY FACE ABOUT ALL THIS.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.17,0:11:56.38,Main,,0,0,0,,AND HOPEFULLY, THAT'LL WORK.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.47,0:11:58.63,Main,,0,0,0,,- Fukuhara:\NSO THE WAR WITH CLASS D
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.72,0:12:01.30,Main,,0,0,0,,WAS SUCCESSFULLY AVOIDED.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.39,0:12:02.81,Main,,0,0,0,,HOWEVER...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.39,0:12:10.02,Main,,0,0,0,,- BAKA AND TEST.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.27,0:12:13.44,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU GUYS REALLY\NNEED TO LISTEN TO THIS.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.52,0:12:15.86,Main,,0,0,0,,BAD NEWS THE SITUATION\NIS EVEN WORSE NOW
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.94,0:12:17.82,Main,,0,0,0,,THAN IT WAS THIS MORNING.\N- Um, is it really true
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.90,0:12:19.32,Main,,0,0,0,,That you have pictures\Nof Akihisa
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.41,0:12:21.53,Main,,0,0,0,,in a sailor school uniform?\N- $100 each.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.62,0:12:24.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Redistribution is prohibited.\N- Yes, I'll take everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.54,0:12:25.62,Main,,0,0,0,,- OOPS, THAT WASN'T IT.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.70,0:12:27.41,Main,,0,0,0,,- HEY, WHAT THE CRAP!\NYOU'RE RIGHT!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.50,0:12:29.12,Main,,0,0,0,,THE SITUATION HAS GOTTEN\NTOTALLY WORSE.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.21,0:12:30.42,Main,,0,0,0,,- CALM DOWN,\NYOU DON'T HAVE TO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.50,0:12:31.67,Main,,0,0,0,,MAKE A BIG DEAL\NOUT OF EVERYTHING.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.75,0:12:33.09,Main,,0,0,0,,- SOMEONE IS SELLING\NPICTURES OF ME
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.17,0:12:35.59,Main,,0,0,0,,LIKE I WAS HIDE-FREAKIN'-YOSHI.\NTHIS IS SO NOT NOTHING!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.67,0:12:37.47,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT? SOMEONE'S SELLING\NPICTURES OF ME?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.55,0:12:38.72,Main,,0,0,0,,I DIDN'T DO ANYTHING.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.80,0:12:40.68,Main,,0,0,0,,WHY IS MY SITUATION\NGETTING WORSE?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.76,0:12:42.10,Main,,0,0,0,,- HERE'S THE REAL ONE.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.18,0:12:44.14,Main,,0,0,0,,- How are things holding up\Nwith Class F?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.22,0:12:45.39,Main,,0,0,0,,- Very good, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.47,0:12:46.85,Main,,0,0,0,,They're not aware\Nof our plans at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.93,0:12:49.18,Main,,0,0,0,,- Perfect, we'll recover our\Nscores in the mean time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.27,0:12:50.81,Main,,0,0,0,,If they notice\Nwhat we're up to,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.89,0:12:53.65,Main,,0,0,0,,we'll declare war immediately.\N- WHAT THE HELL WAS THAT?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.73,0:12:54.86,Main,,0,0,0,,I THOUGHT CLASS D SAID
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.94,0:12:56.28,Main,,0,0,0,,THEY WEREN'T GOING\NTO ATTACK US ANYMORE.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.36,0:12:59.07,Main,,0,0,0,,- NO, THAT ISN'T "D."\NWHERE DID THIS COME FROM, KOUTA?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.15,0:13:01.74,Main,,0,0,0,,- I RECORDED IT\NIN CLASS "B."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.82,0:13:04.91,Main,,0,0,0,,- DAMN, THAT NEMOTO GUY\NPLAYS ALMOST AS DIRTY AS SHOUKO.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.99,0:13:06.24,Main,,0,0,0,,- BUT WHY THE HELL\NWOULD CLASS B
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.33,0:13:07.66,Main,,0,0,0,,WANT TO DECLARE WAR ON US?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.75,0:13:10.54,Main,,0,0,0,,- HE LOST A LOT OF RESPECT\NAFTER THAT LAST S.T. WAR.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.62,0:13:12.71,Main,,0,0,0,,- ON TOP OF THAT,\NHE GOT THEM TO AGREE
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.79,0:13:14.42,Main,,0,0,0,,TO PARTICIPATE IN\NTHE PEEKING OPERATION,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.50,0:13:15.59,Main,,0,0,0,,WHICH FAILED MISERABLY.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.67,0:13:17.34,Main,,0,0,0,,- WITH ALL THAT DRAMA,\NHE PROBABLY LOST
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.42,0:13:19.22,Main,,0,0,0,,THE CONTROL HE HAD\NOVER HIS OWN CLASSROOM.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.30,0:13:20.92,Main,,0,0,0,,I'M GUESSING THIS\NIS ALL A PLOY
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.01,0:13:23.09,Main,,0,0,0,,TO CALM DOWN THE CLASS,\NSO HE CAN TAKE OVER AGAIN.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.18,0:13:25.39,Main,,0,0,0,,HE MUST BE PLANNING\NTO CREATE A NEW ENEMY FOR THEM
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.47,0:13:26.85,Main,,0,0,0,,BY DIRECTING\NTHEIR ANGST AT US.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.93,0:13:28.31,Main,,0,0,0,,MAYBE THEN, THEY WON'T\NBE PISSED AT HIM
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.39,0:13:29.56,Main,,0,0,0,,FOR BEING SUCH A FAILURE.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.64,0:13:30.77,Main,,0,0,0,,- IF HE CAN PULL IT OFF,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.85,0:13:32.27,Main,,0,0,0,,IT'LL MOST LIKELY\NHELP HIM REGAIN
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.35,0:13:33.90,Main,,0,0,0,,SOME OF THE GROUND HE LOST.\N- NO.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.98,0:13:35.27,Main,,0,0,0,,WE HAVEN'T RECOVERED\NOUR SCORES YET.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.36,0:13:36.82,Main,,0,0,0,,IF CLASS B\NDECIDES TO ATTACK US,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.90,0:13:38.74,Main,,0,0,0,,THERE'S NO FRICKIN' WAY\NWE CAN BEAT THEM.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.82,0:13:41.32,Main,,0,0,0,,- I REALIZE THAT, SO NOW WE\NHAVE TO CREATE A SITUATION
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.40,0:13:43.45,Main,,0,0,0,,WHERE CLASS B WON'T BE ABLE\NTO DECLARE WAR ON US.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.53,0:13:45.37,Main,,0,0,0,,- SO WHAT ARE WE\NSUPPOSED TO DO NOW?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.45,0:13:47.53,Main,,0,0,0,,- THAT'S EASY.  ALL WE NEED\NIS FOR ANOTHER CLASSROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.62,0:13:49.75,Main,,0,0,0,,TO DECLARE WAR ON US\NBEFORE THEY GET A CHANCE TO.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.83,0:13:51.71,Main,,0,0,0,,- ARE YOU KIDDING ME?\N- NO, I'M NOT.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.79,0:13:53.58,Main,,0,0,0,,WE NEED TO ENTER INTO\NBATTLE WITH CLASS "D."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.67,0:13:56.21,Main,,0,0,0,,- OH MY GOD! WE JUST WENT\NTHROUGH ALL THAT TROUBLE
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.29,0:13:58.21,Main,,0,0,0,,TO KEEP D FROM\NSTARTING A WAR WITH US.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.30,0:14:00.05,Main,,0,0,0,,- IT DOESN'T MATTER\NWHO WE GO UP AGAINST.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.13,0:14:02.01,Main,,0,0,0,,IF WE'RE FIGHT AN S.T. WAR,\NWE'LL BE GIVEN TIME
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.09,0:14:04.09,Main,,0,0,0,,TO RECOUP OUR SCORES\NWITH THE RECOVERY TESTS.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.18,0:14:05.64,Main,,0,0,0,,IT MAKES MORE SENSE\NFOR US TO DO THAT
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.72,0:14:07.60,Main,,0,0,0,,AFTER LOSING TO CLASS D\NINSTEAD OF "B."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.68,0:14:09.77,Main,,0,0,0,,- I THINK I GET IT.\NIF WE TAKE THE REMEDIAL CLASS
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.85,0:14:11.98,Main,,0,0,0,,AND GET OUR SCORES UP,\NCLASS B IS LESS LIKELY
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.06,0:14:14.19,Main,,0,0,0,,TO WANT TO ATTACK US, RIGHT?\N- BUT, YUUJI,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.27,0:14:16.94,Main,,0,0,0,,WITH OUR CURRENT SCORES,\NWE CAN'T EVEN DEFEAT CLASS "D."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.02,0:14:17.98,Main,,0,0,0,,- I KNOW, BUT DON'T WORRY.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.07,0:14:19.65,Main,,0,0,0,,I THINK I'VE GOT\NA SOLUTION FOR THAT.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.73,0:14:21.24,Main,,0,0,0,,FIRST THINGS FIRST, THOUGH.\NSOMEHOW, WE NEED
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.32,0:14:23.45,Main,,0,0,0,,TO GET CLASS D TO DECLARE\NWAR ON US LIKE PRONTO.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.53,0:14:24.74,Main,,0,0,0,,- OKAY, HOW?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.82,0:14:26.70,Main,,0,0,0,,- WE CAN USE WHAT\NHAPPENED THIS MORNING.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.78,0:14:28.41,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU AND MINAMI\NJUST GET ALL COZY
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.49,0:14:30.25,Main,,0,0,0,,AND PISS OFF MIHARU.\N- WHAT?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.33,0:14:32.08,Main,,0,0,0,,- I DON'T THINK SO.\NNO WAY.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.16,0:14:33.41,Main,,0,0,0,,- Yuuji: CAN'T YOU RECONSIDER?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.50,0:14:35.50,Main,,0,0,0,,- NEVER IN A MILLION YEARS.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.58,0:14:37.38,Main,,0,0,0,,PLUS, NO ONE'S GONNA BELIEVE
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.46,0:14:39.38,Main,,0,0,0,,I WOULD BE THE GIRLFRIEND\NOF SUCH A STUPID IDIOT.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.46,0:14:41.17,Main,,0,0,0,,- COME ON.  YOU KNOW\NYOU'RE THE ONLY ONE
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.26,0:14:43.88,Main,,0,0,0,,WHO CAN DO THIS, MINAMI.\NIF CLASS B ATTACKS US NOW,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.97,0:14:46.05,Main,,0,0,0,,WE'RE GONNA HAVE TO GO BACK\NTO USING CARDBOARD BOXES.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.14,0:14:48.05,Main,,0,0,0,,DO YOU REALLY WANT THAT?\N- YEAH, AND NOT TO MENTION
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.14,0:14:50.76,Main,,0,0,0,,HIMEJI'S PARENTS MIGHT GET\NSUPER WORRIED ABOUT HER AGAIN.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.85,0:14:53.68,Main,,0,0,0,,DO YOU REALLY WANT THEM TO\NTRANSFER HER TO ANOTHER SCHOOL?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.77,0:14:55.73,Main,,0,0,0,,- OH, AND WE COULD USE\NYOUR HELP TOO, HIMEJI.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.81,0:14:57.11,Main,,0,0,0,,- BUT WHAT CAN I DO?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.19,0:14:59.65,Main,,0,0,0,,- WE DON'T THINK MINAMI\NACTING THIS ALL BY HERSELF
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.73,0:15:01.07,Main,,0,0,0,,WILL BE CONVINCING ENOUGH.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.15,0:15:02.36,Main,,0,0,0,,WO WE WERE HOPING\NYOU COULD PRETEND
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.44,0:15:04.99,Main,,0,0,0,,THAT YOU WERE JEALOUS\NOF THEIR RELATIONSHIP.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.45,0:15:09.53,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT DO YOU THINK?\NYOU CAN MANAGE THAT,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.62,0:15:10.91,Main,,0,0,0,,CAN'T YOU?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.29,0:15:16.04,Main,,0,0,0,,- I, UM-- LOOK,\NMINAMI AND AKIHISA,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.12,0:15:18.21,Main,,0,0,0,,I UNDERSTAND YOU\NMAY NOT WANT TO DO THIS,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.29,0:15:19.63,Main,,0,0,0,,BUT YOU HAVE TO.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.71,0:15:20.71,Main,,0,0,0,,- MIZUKI.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.79,0:15:22.05,Main,,0,0,0,,- I'M SORRY.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.13,0:15:24.09,Main,,0,0,0,,I KNOW I'M BEING SELFISH,\NBUT I CAN'T HELP IT.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.17,0:15:25.76,Main,,0,0,0,,I JUST REALLY DON'T\NWANT MY PARENTS
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.84,0:15:27.76,Main,,0,0,0,,TO MAKE ME CHANGE SCHOOLS.\NPLEASE DO THIS.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.84,0:15:31.43,Main,,0,0,0,,- WELL, I GUESS SINCE\NI'LL JUST BE FAKING IT,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.51,0:15:32.51,Main,,0,0,0,,IT'S NOT THAT\NBIG OF A DEAL.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.60,0:15:34.14,Main,,0,0,0,,- THANK YOU SO MUCH, MINAMI.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.23,0:15:35.89,Main,,0,0,0,,- LOVELY, NOW\NLET'S GET STARTED.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.98,0:15:37.94,Main,,0,0,0,,- ALL RIGHT, WHAT'S THIS?\NLIKE A SCRIPT?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.02,0:15:40.77,Main,,0,0,0,,- "SORRY FOR ASKING YOU\NTO COME SEE ME LIKE THIS,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.86,0:15:44.07,Main,,0,0,0,,BUT I WANTED YOU TO KNOW\NTHAT I'M IN LOVE WITH YOU."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.15,0:15:45.82,Main,,0,0,0,,- "I HAVE A CONFESSION\NFOR YOU TOO.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.90,0:15:48.11,Main,,0,0,0,,I FEEL THE SAME WA--"\NOH NO, NO, NO, NO.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.20,0:15:50.08,Main,,0,0,0,,- I AM SO NOT\NSAYING ANY OF THAT!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.16,0:15:52.74,Main,,0,0,0,,- I KNOW IT'S JUST PRETEND,\NBUT THIS IS EMBARRASSING.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.83,0:15:54.12,Main,,0,0,0,,- WATCH ME DO IT.\NYOU'RE NOT
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.20,0:15:55.33,Main,,0,0,0,,GETTING INTO YOUR CHARACTERS.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.41,0:15:56.79,Main,,0,0,0,,- Aki: WHAT?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.87,0:15:57.79,Main,,0,0,0,,- Fukuhara: WOW.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.59,0:16:08.76,Main,,0,0,0,,- I'M SORRY FOR ASKING YOU\NTO COME SEE ME LIKE THIS.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.84,0:16:12.35,Main,,0,0,0,,BUT I WANTED YOU TO KNOW\NTHAT I'M IN LOVE WITH YOU.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.43,0:16:14.64,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT?\N- EVER SINCE I FIRST MET YOU,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.72,0:16:17.43,Main,,0,0,0,,I'VE BEEN IN LOVE WITH YOU.\NIT WAS REALLY HARD FOR ME
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.52,0:16:19.44,Main,,0,0,0,,TO BE NO MORE THAN A FRIEND\NTO YOU THIS WHOLE TIME.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.52,0:16:22.77,Main,,0,0,0,,THE TRUTH IS I CAN'T BEAR\NTO BE JUST FRIENDS
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.86,0:16:24.07,Main,,0,0,0,,WITH YOU ANY LONGER.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.20,0:16:30.12,Main,,0,0,0,,AKI, I KNOW THIS\NMUST BE WEIRD TO HEAR
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.20,0:16:31.70,Main,,0,0,0,,AFTER WHAT I SAID\NTO YOU EARLIER,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.78,0:16:33.74,Main,,0,0,0,,BUT PLEASE UNDERSTAND.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.83,0:16:36.66,Main,,0,0,0,,I AM MADLY\NIN LOVE WITH YOU.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.75,0:16:38.96,Main,,0,0,0,,WOULD YOU LIKE\NTO BE MY BOYFRIEND?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.34,0:16:45.30,Main,,0,0,0,,SO SOMETHING LIKE THAT.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.38,0:16:47.17,Main,,0,0,0,,- WOW, THAT WAS BEAUTIFUL.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.26,0:16:48.38,Main,,0,0,0,,- MY HEART IS STILL RACING.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.63,0:16:52.10,Main,,0,0,0,,- HEY, WHAT'S WRONG\NWITH YOU, DUDE?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.18,0:16:54.05,Main,,0,0,0,,- I JUST NEED A MOMENT.\NCOULD YOU DO ME A FAVOR
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.14,0:16:55.64,Main,,0,0,0,,AND LEAVE ME ALONE\NFOR A LITTLE BIT?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.72,0:16:58.98,Main,,0,0,0,,I DON'T WANT TO WAKE UP\NFROM THIS DREAM, NOT YET.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.06,0:17:00.73,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( sighs )\NYOU'RE UP, KOUTA.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.81,0:17:02.77,Main,,0,0,0,,THINK YOU CAN PUT\NMIHARU'S WIRETAP DEVICE
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.86,0:17:04.61,Main,,0,0,0,,BACK UP ON THE ROOFTOP?\N- I CAN DO THAT.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.69,0:17:06.86,Main,,0,0,0,,- I WANT THE THREE OF YOU TO\NHEAD UP THERE AND PUT ON A SHOW,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.94,0:17:08.65,Main,,0,0,0,,SO MIHARU THAT WILL HEAR IT\NTHROUGH THE MICROPHONE
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.74,0:17:10.32,Main,,0,0,0,,AND GET THE WRONG IDEA.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.40,0:17:13.53,Main,,0,0,0,,- THE SETUP IS THAT AKIHISA\NAND MINAMI ARE MEETING SECRETLY.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.62,0:17:15.70,Main,,0,0,0,,OKAY, NOW LINK\NYOUR ARMS TOGETHER.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.79,0:17:17.41,Main,,0,0,0,,- UH... HOW COME?\N- OUR ARMS?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.49,0:17:19.16,Main,,0,0,0,,- WE GOT TO MAKE THIS\NLOOK AUTHENTIC,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.25,0:17:20.83,Main,,0,0,0,,ESPECIALLY AFTER WHAT HAPPENED,\NSO DO IT.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.91,0:17:22.83,Main,,0,0,0,,- I'M IN.  GIVE ME YOUR ARM.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.92,0:17:24.63,Main,,0,0,0,,- IF YOU TRY TO TOUCH ME\NANYWHERE ELSE, I'LL KILL YOU.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.84,0:17:29.09,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( students chatter )
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.92,0:17:32.38,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( nervous laughs )
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.47,0:17:33.97,Main,,0,0,0,,WHEN YOU GRAB AHOLD\NOF ME THAT TIGHT,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.05,0:17:36.18,Main,,0,0,0,,IT'S HARD TO WALK.\N- WE'RE SUPPOSED TO BE DATING,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.26,0:17:38.27,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU DUMMY.\NTHIS IS CALLED NORMAL BEHAVIOR.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.35,0:17:40.10,Main,,0,0,0,,- I GET THAT, BUT\NYOUR YOU-KNOW-WHATS
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.18,0:17:41.19,Main,,0,0,0,,ARE DIGGING INTO MY ELBOW.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.27,0:17:43.98,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( gasps )\NYOU'RE DIRTY.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.06,0:17:45.32,Main,,0,0,0,,- IT'S YOUR RIBS.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.40,0:17:47.07,Main,,0,0,0,,( screams )\NOH, CRAP.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.15,0:17:48.23,Main,,0,0,0,,I'M SUPPOSED TO BE ACTING.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.32,0:17:49.36,Main,,0,0,0,,UM...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.44,0:17:50.57,Main,,0,0,0,,- YES, DEAR?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.65,0:17:52.53,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT IS IT EXACTLY\NYOU LIKE ABOUT ME?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.61,0:17:54.24,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHY ARE YOU ASKING?\NISN'T IT OBVIOUS?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.32,0:17:56.62,Main,,0,0,0,,EVERYTHING FROM\NTHE TOP OF YOUR HEAD TO--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.70,0:17:59.70,Main,,0,0,0,,- TO WHAT?\N- YOUR EYEBROWS.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.79,0:18:02.21,Main,,0,0,0,,- MY FOREHEAD?\NI GUESS THAT MAKES SENSE.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.29,0:18:07.38,Main,,0,0,0,,- I HAVE TO ASK.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.46,0:18:08.84,Main,,0,0,0,,WHY ARE YOUR ARMS\NCROSSED LIKE THAT?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.92,0:18:12.01,Main,,0,0,0,,- MIZUKI?\N- YOU'RE SO CLOSE TO EACH OTHER.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.09,0:18:14.34,Main,,0,0,0,,IT ALMOST LOOKS LIKE-- LIKE...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.43,0:18:17.35,Main,,0,0,0,,LIKE THE TWO OF YOU MIGHT\NBE DATING OR SOMETHING.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.43,0:18:20.89,Main,,0,0,0,,- WAIT, WAS THAT LINE\NIN THE SCRIPT?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.97,0:18:22.89,Main,,0,0,0,,OH, SHE'S IMPROVISING.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.98,0:18:24.52,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU'RE RIGHT, MIZUKI.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.60,0:18:26.31,Main,,0,0,0,,AKIHISA AND I\NARE INDEED TOGETHER.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.40,0:18:28.69,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHY DIDN'T YOU\NTELL ME ABOUT THIS?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.78,0:18:32.44,Main,,0,0,0,,- I'M SORRY, I SHOULD\NHAVE SAID SOMETHING EARLIER.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.53,0:18:34.07,Main,,0,0,0,,- SO I WAS RIGHT.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.15,0:18:37.78,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU REALLY HAD A THING\NFOR AKIHISA THIS WHOLE TIME.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.87,0:18:40.24,Main,,0,0,0,,- YES, AND I'M SORRY\NFOR KEEPING THAT FROM YOU.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.33,0:18:42.66,Main,,0,0,0,,ESPECIALLY SINCE\NI KNEW HOW YOU FELT.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.75,0:18:44.08,Main,,0,0,0,,I REALLY AM SORRY.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.16,0:18:45.83,Main,,0,0,0,,PLEASE SAY YOU'LL\NBE ABLE TO FORGIVE ME.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.92,0:18:49.17,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU KNOW, I SORT OF\NALREADY KNEW YOU LIKED HIM,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.25,0:18:51.92,Main,,0,0,0,,BUT I DO FEEL BETTER NOW\NTHAT YOU'VE BEEN HONEST WITH ME.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.01,0:18:53.26,Main,,0,0,0,,I UNDERSTAND.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.34,0:18:54.80,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU WERE IN\NAN AWFUL POSITION.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.88,0:18:56.76,Main,,0,0,0,,I DON'T KNOW IF I WOULD\NHAVE SAID ANYTHING EITHER.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.85,0:18:59.31,Main,,0,0,0,,- DOES THAT MEAN\NYOU'RE GONNA FORGIVE ME?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.39,0:19:02.68,Main,,0,0,0,,- THIS ISN'T ABOUT\NWHETHER OR NOT I'LL FORGIVE YOU.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.77,0:19:04.18,Main,,0,0,0,,I THINK YOU SHOULD\NHAVE THE FREEDOM
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.27,0:19:05.94,Main,,0,0,0,,TO LIKE WHOMEVER\NYOU WANT TO LIKE.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.02,0:19:08.27,Main,,0,0,0,,AND I CAN'T FAULT\NYOU FOR THAT, MINAMI,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.36,0:19:10.23,Main,,0,0,0,,ANY MORE THAN\NI COULD FAULT MYSELF.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.32,0:19:13.19,Main,,0,0,0,,- THANK YOU.\N- SURE.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.28,0:19:14.74,Main,,0,0,0,,BUT STILL I--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.82,0:19:16.82,Main,,0,0,0,,I CAN'T FORGIVE YOU FOR\NKISSING HIM THIS MORNING.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.91,0:19:18.28,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU WENT TOO FAR!\NAND ON TOP OF THAT,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.37,0:19:20.29,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU STOLE THE VERY FIRST KISS\NHE WILL EVER HAVE.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.37,0:19:21.62,Main,,0,0,0,,- BUT WE ALREADY\NEXPLAINED THAT WAS
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.70,0:19:23.08,Main,,0,0,0,,BECAUSE OF\NTHE EMAIL AND STUFF.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.16,0:19:24.75,Main,,0,0,0,,- DON'T YOU "AND STUFF" ME.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.83,0:19:26.37,Main,,0,0,0,,GOD, MAY BE ABLE\NTO LET THAT ONE GO,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.46,0:19:27.96,Main,,0,0,0,,BUT I WILL NEVER FORGIVE\NEITHER ONE OF YOU.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.04,0:19:31.88,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( gasps )\NNO, IT'S A WIRETAP THINGY.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.96,0:19:34.38,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU GUYS ARE STUPID.  STUPID!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.47,0:19:36.88,Main,,0,0,0,,- IF HIMEJI SPILLS THE BEANS\NWITHOUT NOTICING IT,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.97,0:19:38.47,Main,,0,0,0,,MIHARU COULD FIGURE\NOUT THE TRUTH.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.97,0:19:42.10,Main,,0,0,0,,- HIMEJI, WAIT!\N- HEY, HOLD UP!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.18,0:19:43.35,Main,,0,0,0,,WHAT'S GOING ON?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.43,0:19:45.06,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU DON'T HAVE\NTO GO AFTER HER,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.14,0:19:47.19,Main,,0,0,0,,UNLESS YOU'RE GONNA\NPICK HER OVER ME.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.27,0:19:48.48,Main,,0,0,0,,- I'M SORRY, MINAMI.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.56,0:19:51.15,Main,,0,0,0,,BUT THERE'S SOMETHING\NI HAVE TO TAKE CARE OF.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.23,0:19:53.48,Main,,0,0,0,,- NO, YOU CAN'T LEAVE ME.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.57,0:19:56.45,Main,,0,0,0,,AKI, PLEASE, I HAVE\NSOMETHING I WANT TO TELL YOU.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.03,0:20:01.08,Main,,0,0,0,,I THINK I'M\NIN LOVE WITH YOU.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.16,0:20:06.12,Main,,0,0,0,,FINALLY, I SAID IT.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.92,0:20:11.50,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT THE HELL\NWAS THAT ALL ABOUT?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.59,0:20:13.34,Main,,0,0,0,,THERE'S A SCRIPT, YOU KNOW?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.42,0:20:16.47,Main,,0,0,0,,- YEAH, DON'T WORRY.\NI'M DONE ACTING.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.55,0:20:19.47,Main,,0,0,0,,EVERYONE KNOWS\NAKI LIKES GIRLY-GIRLS.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.55,0:20:21.35,Main,,0,0,0,,SO THIS HAS JUST\NBEEN A WASTE OF TIME.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.77,0:20:26.56,Main,,0,0,0,,- Aki: HIMEJI.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.98,0:20:32.23,Main,,0,0,0,,- OH, HI, AKIHISA.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.66,0:20:43.54,Main,,0,0,0,,I DIDN'T EVEN KNOW\NTHAT THING WAS THERE.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.62,0:20:45.91,Main,,0,0,0,,THANKS SO MUCH\NFOR SAVING ME AGAIN.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.99,0:20:47.96,Main,,0,0,0,,- ARE YOU FEELING OKAY, HIMEJI?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.04,0:20:49.96,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU SEEM LIKE YOU MIGHT\NBE A LITTLE BUMMED.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.04,0:20:51.46,Main,,0,0,0,,- OH, NO, DO\NI LOOK THAT BAD?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.54,0:20:53.84,Main,,0,0,0,,- WELL, NOT BAD,\NMAYBE A LITTLE LONELY.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.92,0:20:56.13,Main,,0,0,0,,- I WONDER WHAT\NTHAT LOOKS LIKE.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.21,0:20:58.01,Main,,0,0,0,,IF I DO LOOK LONELY,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.09,0:20:59.97,Main,,0,0,0,,IT'S PROBABLY BECAUSE\NI'M A LITTLE SAD.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.05,0:21:01.51,Main,,0,0,0,,EVEN IF IT WAS\NONLY FOR SHOW,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.59,0:21:03.22,Main,,0,0,0,,I STILL FEEL LIKE\NTHE PERSON I LIKE
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.30,0:21:05.10,Main,,0,0,0,,WAS TAKEN AWAY FROM ME.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.18,0:21:08.02,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU KNOW WHAT I MEAN,\NDON'T YOU?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.10,0:21:10.14,Main,,0,0,0,,- OF COURSE I UNDERSTAND\NWHAT YOU MEAN.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.23,0:21:11.48,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU WERE JUST GETTING\NINTO CHARACTER.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.56,0:21:14.11,Main,,0,0,0,,- I GUESS THAT'S RIGHT.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.19,0:21:16.03,Main,,0,0,0,,IT'S LIKE HIDEYOSHI SAID.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.11,0:21:18.11,Main,,0,0,0,,- I MIGHT BE\NA LITTLE JEALOUS TOO.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.19,0:21:19.32,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.40,0:21:20.99,Main,,0,0,0,,- IF YOU AND MINAMI LIKED\NTHE SAME GUY,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.07,0:21:23.20,Main,,0,0,0,,IT WOULD BUG ME, EVEN IF\NYOU WERE PRETENDING.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.79,0:21:27.45,Main,,0,0,0,,- JUST FOR FUNSIES,\NLET'S SAY
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.54,0:21:29.16,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU WERE IN THAT\NEXACT SITUATION.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.25,0:21:31.21,Main,,0,0,0,,WHAT WOULD YOU DO\NABOUT IT, AKIHISA?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.29,0:21:34.04,Main,,0,0,0,,- WELL, LET ME SEE.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.13,0:21:37.30,Main,,0,0,0,,I GUESS I WOULD MOST LIKELY\NTHINK REALLY HARD ABOUT IT.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.38,0:21:40.22,Main,,0,0,0,,- WAIT, YOU WOULD MOST LIKELY\NTHINK ABOUT IT?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.30,0:21:43.26,Main,,0,0,0,,- YEAH, I'D THINK REALLY HARD\NABOUT IT IN MY OWN WAY.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.35,0:21:45.85,Main,,0,0,0,,AND THEN BE LIKE WAY HONEST\NWITH EVERYTHING.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.93,0:21:47.77,Main,,0,0,0,,- BUT I WANTED YOU\NTO TELL ME
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.85,0:21:49.93,Main,,0,0,0,,WHICH ONE OF US\NYOU WOULD PICK.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.02,0:21:52.02,Main,,0,0,0,,WHAT? OH NO,\NI DIDN'T SAY ANYTHING.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.10,0:21:55.23,Main,,0,0,0,,- I WAS PRETTY SURPRISED THOUGH.\N- YOU WERE? ABOUT WHAT?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.32,0:21:57.15,Main,,0,0,0,,- WELL, IT'S JUST THAT THE WAY\NYOU WERE TALKING EARLIER,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.23,0:21:58.53,Main,,0,0,0,,DIDN'T MAKE IT SEEM\NLIKE YOU WERE ACTING.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.61,0:22:00.24,Main,,0,0,0,,I THOUGHT YOU MIGHT-- YOU KNOW.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.03,0:22:05.28,Main,,0,0,0,,DID YOU USE TO PERFORM\NIN PLAYS OR SOMETHING?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.54,0:22:10.83,Main,,0,0,0,,WHERE ARE YOU GOING?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.54,0:22:13.54,Main,,0,0,0,,- IDIOT.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.46,0:22:17.63,Main,,0,0,0,,- DUMMY.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.30,0:22:24.18,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( theme music plays )
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.26,0:22:25.43,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( singing in Japanese )
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.31,0:23:53.22,Main,,0,0,0,,- Fukuhara: QUESTION 10:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.31,0:23:55.14,Main,,0,0,0,,"NAME THE NUTRIENTS MISO LACKS
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.23,0:23:56.73,Main,,0,0,0,,AS WELL AS SUITABLE INGREDIENTS
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.81,0:23:58.81,Main,,0,0,0,,THAT COULD MAKE UP\NFOR THE LACKING NUTRIENTS."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.90,0:24:01.48,Main,,0,0,0,,- Mizuki: VITAMIN C, ORANGE,\NAND HYDROCHLORIC ACID.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.57,0:24:03.44,Main,,0,0,0,,- THAT IS NOT ACCURATE.\N- Aki: NEXT EPISODE,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.53,0:24:04.57,Main,,0,0,0,,"ME, ROMANCE,\NAND LOVE SKILLS."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.65,0:24:06.40,Main,,0,0,0,,- Fukuhara:\NTHIS WILL BE ON THE TEST.
